00035 // Make it easy to access the keycodes (with same syntax as before)
00036 // rbs -- CastPtrToLong avoids warnings when casting a void* to a long value. 
00037 // don't use it on something that is really a pointer! 
00038 // perhaps at some point we should move CastPtrToLong() somewhere else.
00039 #ifdef MAC_VERSION
00040 #define CastPtrToLong(x)        ((long)(x))
00041 #endif
00042 #ifdef WIN_VERSION
00043 #define CastPtrToLong(x)        (PtrToLong(x))
00044 #endif
00045 #define JKEY_RETURN             (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_return->s_thing))
00046 #define JKEY_ENTER              (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_enter->s_thing))
00047 #define JKEY_SPACEBAR           (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_spacebar->s_thing))
00048 #define JKEY_BACKSPACE          (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_backspace->s_thing))
00049 #define JKEY_BACKSLASH          (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_backslash->s_thing))
00050 #define JKEY_VERTBAR                (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_vertbar->s_thing))
00051 #define JKEY_GRAVE              (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_grave->s_thing))
00052 #define JKEY_TILDE              (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_tilde->s_thing))
00053 #define JKEY_TAB                    (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_tab->s_thing))
00054 #define JKEY_CLEAR              (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_clear->s_thing))
00055 #define JKEY_ESC                    (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_esc->s_thing))
00056 #define JKEY_OPTIONSPACE            (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_optionspace->s_thing))
00057 #define JKEY_LEFTARROW          (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_leftarrow->s_thing))
00058 #define JKEY_RIGHTARROW         (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_rightarrow->s_thing))
00059 #define JKEY_UPARROW                (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_uparrow->s_thing))
00060 #define JKEY_DOWNARROW          (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_downarrow->s_thing))
00061 #define JKEY_HOME               (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_home->s_thing))
00062 #define JKEY_END                    (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_end->s_thing))
00063 #define JKEY_PAGEUP             (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_pageup->s_thing))
00064 #define JKEY_PAGEDOWN           (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_pagedown->s_thing))
00065 #define JKEY_HELPKEY                (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_helpkey->s_thing))
00066 #define JKEY_DELETE             (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_delete->s_thing))
00067 #define JKEY_INSERT             (CastPtrToLong(ps_key_insert->s_thing))
